          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（贾宝玉上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "迈步出离怡红院，\n想起金钏愁顿添。\n逼死姣娃丧黄泉。\n只落得花容月貌顷刻捐。\n再不能谈心绛云轩。\n满腹心事对谁言。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳，早知今日，悔不当初。想我贾宝玉，每日在大观园中，不是听林妹妹之弹\n琴，就是同宝姐姐吟诗，无论风花雪月，那一件不是尽兴玩耍，谁想还是人心\n不足，贪得无厌。昨日到了太太房中，与金钏姐姐取笑了几句，不料被太太碰\n见，以为是她引诱于我，一怒将她赶出府去，因此她羞恨交加，投井而死，这\n不是明明被我所害么。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "叫头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "金钏姐姐！"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你死得这样惨苦，叫我日后到了九泉之下，有何面目，与你相见哪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "事到伤心泪自多，\n红颜薄命可奈何。\n我的金……"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（贾政暗上，看。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾政",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾政",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "你为何背地伤心泪婆娑？"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾政",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你方才言讲“金”什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "“金”么……是孩儿见扇上，金坠失丢，故而在此沉吟。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾政",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我把你这畜生，还有哪些不足？终日不是寻愁觅恨，就是长吁短叹，真乃是不\n长进的东西！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（家院上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "家院",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启禀老爷：今有忠顺王府长史求见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾政",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是了。\n有客到来，你且退下。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命。\n好了好了，这回重责，业已逃过，待我且到潇湘馆，与林妹妹玩耍便了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（贾宝玉下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾政",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呵，忠顺王府，向无来往，今日使人前来，必有原故。"
        },
        {
          "character": "家院、家院",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾政",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吩咐动乐有请。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王府长史、四监、二家将同上。王府长史与贾政见礼。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾政",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不知大人驾到，有失远迎，望祈恕罪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王府长史",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岂敢那，岂敢。下官来此，并非擅造潭府，只因我府有一个戏子，名叫琪官，\n一向好好的在府伺候，如今竟三五日，靡有回去，因此各处查访。谁想这满京\n城里，十停人，倒有八停人，说那戏子，近日和含玉而生的那位令郎，相交甚\n厚。下官因为是在老先生府上，不敢擅来索讨，所以回了王爷。王爷的意思，\n若是别的戏子，就是一百个，也就罢了，只是这个琪官，在王爷面前，随机应\n变，甚合其意，断断少他不得。故命下官前来相求，望祈老先生转达令郎，将\n琪官放回，不但王爷领情，下官也免奔劳之苦。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（贾政作又惊又气。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾政",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呵，竟有这等事，大人少待，待学生叫出小儿，当面追问。\n人来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "家院",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "伺候老爷。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾政",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "速到大观园，将宝玉传来见我。"
        },
        {
          "character": "家院",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。\n老爷有命，传宝二爷问话。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（贾宝玉上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "西皮正板",
          "musical_style": "西皮正板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "在潇湘，伴颦卿，\n忽听传唤胆战惊。\n见了父亲问分明。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呼唤孩儿，有何吩咐？"
        },
        {
          "character": "急忙且把衣冠整、贾政",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗯嗯嗯，你这畜生，不在家用心读书，已应重责，怎敢又做出无法无天的事来。\n那琪官，乃是忠顺王爷驾前承奉，你竟敢将他引诱出来，如今祸及于我，快\n快从实讲来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孩儿不但不知此事，并连这“琪官”二字，也不知晓。此等言语，叫孩儿怎样\n承认？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王府长史",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "公子不必隐瞒了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "实在不知，并非虚语。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王府长史",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "既是公子不知，腰中那条红汗巾子，可是哪儿来的呢？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（贾宝玉惊。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "叫头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，大人吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听说他在紫檀堡，置买房产，想在那里，也未可知。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾政",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你且去到书房，等我送客回来，有话问你。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳，不知他从哪里，打听得这样详细。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（贾宝玉下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王府长史",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "令郎如此说来，一定是在紫檀堡。下官且去寻找，若在那里便罢，若不在那里，\n还要前来请教，一切冒犯，当面谢过。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾政",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不敢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王府长史",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "告辞了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾政",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王府长史",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "事非得已奉差遣，\n登门打扰求海涵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾政",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "接待不周多怠慢，\n恭送大人到门前。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王府长史",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "手拉着先生回身转，"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾政",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "替学生代问王爷安。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
