    {
      "scene_index": 4,
      "label": "第四场",
      "characters_present": [
        "婆子",
        "贾宝玉"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（贾宝玉上，走串子。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，且住，看我父亲，这样光景，一定是要将我重重责打。咳，吓，有了，\n若是我那宝姐姐、林妹妹在此，一定与我出个主意，无奈她们又不知晓。咳，\n就是那焙茗小子在此，也能给老太太送信，前来打救于我，偏偏他又不在跟前。\n但说是这这……"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（乱劈柴。婆子上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "婆子",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "急急忙忙，去到厨房。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好了好了，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（贾宝玉拉婆子。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你快去告诉老太太，就说老爷要将我打死。"
        },
        {
          "character": "婆子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "金钏不是打死的，她原是跳井死的，没有事了，二爷放心罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（贾宝玉打婆子，婆子下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这样紧急之事，偏偏碰着这个老聋婆子，真乃事不凑巧。我且越过书房，去到\n二门以上，使人报于老太太便了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖急急风〗。贾宝玉下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "贾宝玉→婆子",
          "turns": 2
        },
        {
          "edge": "婆子→贾宝玉",
          "turns": 2
        }
      ],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
          "stage_direction": 5,
          "白": 5,
          "念": 1
        },
