    {
      "scene_index": 5,
      "label": "第五场",
      "characters_present": [
        "一般都是你的子",
        "不分皂白打数遍",
        "不由老身泪满腮",
        "人来与我速打点",
        "他学那斑衣戏彩人皆见",
        "你偏听信小人谗",
        "因为何事遭毒打",
        "家院",
        "平日不把书来念",
        "年老多病长闷倦",
        "急急忙忙往前进",
        "明是嫌我多碍眼",
        "琥珀",
        "百般孝顺真如愿",
        "结交小旦非造反",
        "结交王府蒋小旦",
        "若不严行将他管",
        "贾宝玉",
        "贾政",
        "贾母",
        "贾环",
        "身不由己抖衣战",
        "鸳鸯"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖水底鱼〗。贾政、贾环自两边分上，碰，贾政失色。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾政",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你这畜生也敢这样放肆！"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾环",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孩儿原来不敢跑，只因从那东南角上井边经过，见那井旁有一个死人，哎呀，\n头有这么大，身子有这么粗，把我吓的靡有主意，所以才跑了来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾政",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪个跳井，快快讲来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾环",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孩儿闻听人言，是我宝玉哥哥，在太太房中，强奸了金钏丫头，那金钏羞愧不\n过，所以跳井而死。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾政",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你待怎讲？"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾环",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "金钏跳井而死。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（贾政失色。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾政",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奴才呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾政",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "结交琪官罪已盈，\n逼死丫鬟更非轻。\n今日我要施重惩！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（二家丁、贾宝玉同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "忽听爹爹一声唤，\n吓得我心惊胆又寒。\n无计奈何跪平川。"
        },
        {
          "character": "身不由己抖衣战、贾政",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一见畜生怒冲天，\n罪恶满盈难饶宽。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（家丁同打。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾政",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "打死畜生免辱祖先。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，爹爹呀！孩儿年幼无知，作下这不法之事，望爹爹开一线之恩，饶恕这\n次，孩儿从今以后，发愤读书，再也不敢作此苟且之事了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾政",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "住了！今日若不将你这畜生打死，将来必要闯出大祸来，与我重重的打！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（家丁同打。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，爹爹呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今日里将孩儿逼于非命，\n怕的是我祖母知道伤心。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾政",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呸！"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾政",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听一言来怒转增，\n花言巧语显聪明。\n活活要你的命残生！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（贾政打。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾环",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "还有今天来，早就该打。"
        },
        {
          "character": "家院",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老爷息怒，宝二爷打的不能言语了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾政",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳，若不为老太太知道生气，今日一定，将你处死。嗯嗯嗯。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（贾政下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾环",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你回来再打。咱爷们这块新戏就是这一场吃筋，越打越有好，哈，不回来打了，\n待我把你拉出来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（贾环下。鸳鸯、琥珀扶贾母同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾母",
          "line_type": "西皮导板",
          "musical_style": "西皮导板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "忽听鸳鸯报一声，"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾母",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好叫老身吃一惊。\n一到书房看分明。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我儿在哪里？哎呀，宝玉呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾母",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一见宝玉卧尘埃，\n快快醒来说明白。"
        },
        {
          "character": "急急忙忙往前进、不由老身泪满腮、因为何事遭毒打、贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，祖母吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "急急忙忙往前进、不由老身泪满腮、因为何事遭毒打、贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只为环儿进谗言，\n挑拨我父怒冲天。"
        },
        {
          "character": "急急忙忙往前进、不由老身泪满腮、因为何事遭毒打、贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "哭",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "祖母吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "急急忙忙往前进、不由老身泪满腮、因为何事遭毒打、贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "打得我血肉横飞湿衣衫。"
        },
        {
          "character": "不分皂白打数遍、贾母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "不分皂白打数遍、贾母",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "骂声贾环小贼种，\n又叫老身把气生。\n待我与他把理评。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（贾政急上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾政",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "母亲发怒为何情？"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾政",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "母亲为何生气，有话只管吩咐孩儿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你原来和我说话，我倒有话吩咐，只是我没养个好儿子，可叫我和谁说去？"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾政",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "母亲此话，叫儿子如何当得？"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈，我说一句话，你就当不得。你那样下死手的板子，难道宝玉就当得么。你\n这畜生，真算是只知有己，不知有人哪！"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾母",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "手指贾政骂连声，\n打在他身我心疼。\n听信谗言为何情？"
        },
        {
          "character": "一般都是你的子、贾政",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "母亲容禀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "一般都是你的子、贾政",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "非是孩儿信谗言，\n实是畜生太不端。\n调脂弄粉罪难宽。\n逼死金钏丧井泉。\n只怕他惹祸要无边。"
        },
        {
          "character": "平日不把书来念、结交王府蒋小旦、若不严行将他管、贾母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奴才呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "平日不把书来念、结交王府蒋小旦、若不严行将他管、贾母",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "自古道人难活百年，\n老身今已八十三。\n幸亏宝玉他承欢。\n所以是调弄脂粉女扮男。\n早知你屡次要阻拦。\n丫鬟跳井与他无干。\n血口喷他惹祸端。\n故而打他与我观。"
        },
        {
          "character": "年老多病长闷倦、他学那斑衣戏彩人皆见、百般孝顺真如愿、结交小旦非造反、你偏听信小人谗、明是嫌我多碍眼、人来与我速打点、贾政",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "母亲要往哪里去？"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奴才呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾母",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "整顿车马我要回江南。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾政",
          "line_type": "叫头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，母亲！"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾政",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "再不息怒，孩儿跪下了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾政",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "贾政下跪苦哀告，\n尊声老母听根苗：\n罪恶多端难宽饶。\n怕的后来犯天条。\n从今后指望他不把气来淘。\n因此小事气冲九霄。\n望母亲，恕孩儿，并非是听信谗言，原来是教子念切，此心无他，年过半百，\n从无过犯，望求把儿饶，我这是头一遭。\n拜恳母亲把气消。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（鸳鸯、琥珀同跪。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "鸳鸯、琥珀",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "既是老爷苦苦哀告，老太太就该开恩才是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗯嗯嗯，若不念你平日孝顺，一定不能饶你，与我起来罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（贾政、鸳鸯、琥珀同起。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾政",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢过母亲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "快快去罢，不要在此惹我生气。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾政",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孩儿遵命。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（贾政出门。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾政",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳，我母亲这样溺爱，只怕此子，终无成人之望了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（贾政下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "宝玉，看你爹爹已去，你的身体，还疼不疼，出了气没有？"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孙儿身体，虽不甚疼，只是气还不出。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我已将你父亲骂过，还有何气不出？"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此事原非我父亲主意，乃是听了环儿调唆。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老身适才气糊涂了，有些颠三倒四，竟把这畜生忘记了。\n鸳鸯、琥珀与我将环儿找来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鸳鸯、琥珀",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "领命。\n老太太传环三爷进见。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（贾环上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾环",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不用叫，早就等着了。鸳鸯姐姐，老太太叫我，八成是给我好东西吃？"
        },
        {
          "character": "鸳鸯",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不错了。快去吃罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾环",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈，叫我猜着了。\n祖母在上，孙儿叩头。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你这畜生搬弄是非，令你宝哥哥挨打，真乃可恨。"
        }
      ],
